Text:
The Appeal: Georgia's Most Wanted is the upcoming third studio album by American 
rapper Gucci Mane. The album will be released September 28, 2010 on 1017 Brick Squad Records,
Warner Bros. Records and Asylum Records. The album will follow-up last year's The State vs. Radric Davis, 
released just after the Atlanta rapper's incarceration.
